        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <p><b>Context</b>: considering the objectives set in Vision and Scope and user requirements from Software Requirements Specification, it was considered to proceed with the enlisted below functionalities for the  realization of the informational support within the mobile banking application.<br/>
<b>Requirements</b>: </p>
<ul class="alternate" type="square">
	<li>Requirement 1 - to be able to see the current currency exchange rates within the App</li>
	<li>Requirement 2 - to be able to select favorite currencies (exact number -TBD)</li>
	<li>Requirement 3 - to be able to see the historical changes of the currencies over time (max period - TBD)</li>
	<li>Requirement 4 - to be able to see all the world currencies exchange rates in currency tab</li>
</ul>


<p><b>Functionality</b>: A user shall be able to familiarize him/herself with the actual exchange rates right in the Application.</p>

<p><b>Details</b>: The login screen shall include the default currency rates versus UAH, while the specific tab within the App should grant user a possibility to check all the world currency rates against UAH, historical changes over some period of time (TBD), and set-up of custom feature for user's convenience.<br/>
<b>Notes</b>: the idea has been supported by the Program Board at the Program Review meeting on 23 May 2021, the decision adopted is reflected with the Vision and Scope and SRS documents.</p>

